[section#basic.funscope
    [:en] Function scope
    [:zh_CN] 函数作用域
]

[para]
[:en]
[%label[!scope of]]
Labels ([#stmt.label]) have [+function scope [%scope[!function]]] and may be
used anywhere in the function in which they are declared.
[:zh_CN]
[%标号[!～的作用域]]
标号（[#stmt.label]）具有[~函数作用域 [%作用域[!函数～]]]，且可在声明它的函数中
的任意位置使用。

[:en]
Only labels have function scope.
[:zh_CN]
只有标号具有函数作用域。
